{"tid":1954031,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講下你每日食咩","createTime":"2020-04-01T13:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T11:13:27.000Z","uid":241879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"39e810d20341a6d18029158334820db2cdb72010","tid":1954031,"uid":241879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:54:51.000Z","msg":"我自己日日都係食同一樣野 完全諗唔到買咩食<br />\n想知大家平時食咩 攞下靈感<br />\n<br />\n我因爲費事煮所以一日得一餐 就係烏冬/蕎麥麵+ 煎三文魚/蝦<br />\n早起身就會整杯smoothie 如果唔係真係可以全日唔食生果同菜<br />\n近排試左個而家勁hit既dalgona coffee 好飲到上曬癮 一日飲成3-4杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5399a1c7a37767666312be189cfa3a9d2a7d902b","tid":1954031,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"麵麵麵麵，請你食碗麵"},{"pid":"88f18b9538a7aead5b1e0e4cbb965c23ee74d712","tid":1954031,"uid":241879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5399a1c7a37767666312be189cfa3a9d2a7d902b","tid":1954031,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"麵麵麵麵，請你食碗麵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:59:06.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麵麵麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麵麵麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麵"},{"pid":"e6015d8dcffa3ce56cc8204adff21c212221362c","tid":1954031,"uid":127135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"成日都好頹<br />\n經常零食當正餐"},{"pid":"138da115c8413af140b22b89a29b789879165aae","tid":1954031,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"每日只食一餐"},{"pid":"a5a4ba8a2169684b034a889112e8ad4465e0f76d","tid":1954031,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"魚蛋"},{"pid":"179045502c4d863f21fcb4d34a72627aaae48369"